{"word":"David","slug":"david","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>David</b> - king and poet, General References to<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=8&chapter=4&verse=22'>Rth 4:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=16&verse=13'>1Sa 16:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=17&verse=14'>1Sa 17:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=17&verse=50'>1Sa 17:50</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=18&verse=1'>1Sa 18:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=18&verse=29'>1Sa 18:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=7&verse=5'>2Sa 7:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=18&verse=33'>2Sa 18:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=24&verse=1'>2Sa 24:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=2&verse=10'>1Ki 2:10</a><p/><b>--\"Israel's Versatile King\"</b><p/>Beautiful<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=16&verse=12'>1Sa 16:12</a><p/>Divinely Chosen<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=16&verse=13'>1Sa 16:13</a><p/>Courageous<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=17&verse=34'>1Sa 17:34-36</a><p/>A Champion<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=17&verse=40'>1Sa 17:40</a><p/>A great soldier<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=5&verse=7'>2Sa 5:7</a><p/>Forbidden to build the temple, because a man of war<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=28&verse=3'>1Ch 28:3</a><p/>A Poet, see Psalms 8, 19, 23, c. c.<p/>General trend of his life spiritual<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=13&verse=14'>1Sa 13:14 1Ki 15:5</a><p/>Was led by passion to violate the Mosaic law<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=17&verse=17'>De 17:17 2Sa 5:13</a><p/>Yielded to gross sins in a period of ease<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=11&verse=1'>2Sa 11:1-27</a><p/>Was rebuked by the prophet Nathan<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=12&verse=1'>2Sa 12:1-31</a><p/>His repentance and confession<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=51&verse=1'>Ps 51:1-19</a>"}]}